    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a video game, battle with other video games and beat them by carefully selecting characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select an opponent to play with in classic mode and improve your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You lose when all of your video game assets get damaged.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose between attack, fortify, and direct by clicking on each character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The assets make money for you to buy characters and the Burning ones don't t make money.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280370/extras/f8a8f45c751b9d80c0ae8aca92109995.avif?t=1730410018\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280370/extras_big/f8a8f45c751b9d80c0ae8aca92109995.avif?t=1730410018 width=800 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be The Champion</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in tourney mode to be a champion, you need to defeat all other video games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280370/extras/f119cfda89ca429417715a067d91d5fc.poster.avif?t=1730410018\" width=800 height=121 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280370/extras/f119cfda89ca429417715a067d91d5fc.webm?t=1730410018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
